{"tid":1857904,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣知嗰個人係對的人？","createTime":"2020-02-02T11:36:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T06:16:49.000Z","uid":105055,"like":23,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8c54b71b477e6c5df92a3b12018868bbcfeca656","tid":1857904,"uid":105055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:36:04.000Z","msg":"以前好肯定男朋友係我要搵嘅人<br />\n覺得依世要跟住佢<br />\n但係時間愈耐 開始發現佢好似唔係我想搵嘅人<br />\n好多地方我對佢愈嚟愈失望<br />\n佢好似開始唔在乎我感受 <br />\n我覺得佢成日對我好冷淡 甚至黑我臉<br />\n我知我講出嚟又係會嘈 佢都係唔聽<br />\n我係到諗我係咪一世都要跟住佢<br />\n要一直都唔開心<br />\n定係其實咁先係正常？<br />\n到底大家係點知對方係咪啱嘅人？"},{"pid":"5b49a4f55877edba2897f274167546ab2720d215","tid":1857904,"uid":621,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:58:06.000Z","msg":"掏盡幾多光陰 不襯便不襯"},{"pid":"a08ba057fcb0c5be00365c7c5e06f939798c4a0a","tid":1857904,"uid":306009,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:03:18.000Z","msg":"當你唔再諗呢個問題就代表嗰個人係啱嘅人"},{"pid":"d560122e0e9f4609291dbbc6cd9898dd478f1077","tid":1857904,"uid":105055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a08ba057fcb0c5be00365c7c5e06f939798c4a0a","tid":1857904,"uid":306009,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:03:18.000Z","msg":"當你唔再諗呢個問題就代表嗰個人係啱嘅人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T13:21:45.000Z","msg":"最近我不斷咁諗 應該點做"},{"pid":"9be2b2b4a3e6bd556b19f7728d04b72d8c88348d","tid":1857904,"uid":306009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d560122e0e9f4609291dbbc6cd9898dd478f1077","tid":1857904,"uid":105055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a08ba057fcb0c5be00365c7c5e06f939798c4a0a","tid":1857904,"uid":306009,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:03:18.000Z","msg":"當你唔再諗呢個問題就代表嗰個人係啱嘅人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T13:21:45.000Z","msg":"最近我不斷咁諗 應該點做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T13:24:05.000Z","msg":"有冇傾過"},{"pid":"376f12c3e6e8dbad99c6f6ca62475fe80dadb3d2","tid":1857904,"uid":105055,"like":1,"dislike":0